             <summary>
             Get all chapters for current manga.
             </summary>
             <param name="MangaID"></param>
             <returns>List Charpters of this Manga</returns>
             <remarks>
             Sample request:
            
                 POST /GetForManga/1
                 {
                    "MangaID" : 1
                 }
            
